@page "{handler?}"
@model Project24.Pages.AboutModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
    Layout = "_HomeLayout";
}

<div id="about-p24">
    <h2>About Project24</h2>
    <hr />

    <p>
        This is <b>Project24</b> (or more precisely, <b>Project24b</b>), a web application that I made out of free time
        while waiting for the 2023 Monbukagakusho (MEXT) scholarship's Secondary Screening result.
    </p>
    <p>
        The project started out on 31 August 2022 as "<i>Project24</i>", after I had enough with how my father manage his
        clinic. In 4 weeks after that, many planned features had been scrapped (due to my lack of skill in this field)
        but a big feature was added (despite my lack of skill). On 3rd October I decided to change the project to be
        <i>my</i> NAS manager and demote my father's clinic manager to be a "feature", renaming the project to be "<i>Project24b</i>".
    </p>
    <p>
        If you landed on this About page, you must have been <i>my father</i>, <i>my mother</i>, <i>my brother</i>,
        one of my approved-NAS-user, or you just happened to land here through Google Search. Regardless of who you are,
        I hope you find our resource useful and have a good time here.
    </p>
    <br />
    <p>
        If you encounter any bug, please send a <i>Bug Report</i> ticket using the planned link below, or open an
        <a href="https://github.com/3x3y3z3t/Project24/issues">issue</a>.
        <br />
        If you just want to send feedback, or request something, please send a <i>Feedback/Request</i> ticket using the
        planned link below (feature request and resource request all accepted).
    </p>
    <p>
        This project is open-source under the <b>GPL v3 license</b>. You will be able to access the source code
        <b><a href="https://github.com/3x3y3z3t/Project24">here</a></b>.
    </p>
    <p>
        Current version: <b>@Constants.CurrentVersion</b> (<a href="#release-note" id="rel-note-anchor">Release Note</a>)
    </p>

</div>
<br />

<partial name="_About_AboutUs" />

<div id="release-note">
    <h2>
        <a href="#" id="rel-note-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#rel-note-wrapper" style="color: inherit;">
            Release Note
            <span style="font-size: 1.2rem;">(Click to expand)</span>
        </a>
    </h2>
    <hr />

    <div id="rel-note-wrapper" class="collapse">
        <h5><a href="#rel-note-wrapper" id="rel-note-update">Update</a></h5>
        <div id="rel-note-content"> </div>
    </div>

</div>

@section Scripts {
<script>
    $(document).ready(function() {
        $("#rel-note-anchor").on("click", sendAjaxRequestForReleaseNote);
        $("#rel-note-update").on("click", sendAjaxRequestForReleaseNote);
    });

    function sendAjaxRequestForReleaseNote() {
        $.ajax({
            type: 'GET',
            url: 'About/ReleaseNote',
            contentType: false,
            processData: false,
            cache: false,
            success: replaceReleaseNoteContentWithData,
            error: function() {
                window.alert("Error!");
            }
        });
    }

    function replaceReleaseNoteContentWithData(_content) {
        $("#rel-note-content").html(_content);
    }
</script>
}